name: Designer Outlet
directions: The disabled toilet just inside to the right of the west entrance (the one with the childrens play area)
comment: Sometimes there is a bit of a wait and the old people can be a bit rude from time to time but it’s always clean and the radio plays good music through the speakers :))

name: Tallahassee International Airport

name: Crest Cafe

name: Freebirds

name: Target
comment: Family Bathoom

name: Highlands Smokehouse

name: Anytime Fitness
directions: Restrooms are in the back of the facility. Two have private showers. All four are gender neutral.
comment: Gym members can use the facilities 24/7. General public can use the facilities during staffed office hours when the doors are unlocked to the public. You do not need to be a member to use the restrooms during office hours. The gym staff is very friendly and accepting.

name: Dotty’s

name: Walgreens

name: Red Store

name: Irondequoit Bay Marine Park

name: Olympic Cards and Comics
comment: Gabi is a staunch ally!

name: Speedway Gas Station

name: Coral Pine Park

name: Perdido Artist Gallery & Gifts
directions:
“ One block off Sorento Road just one block before the bridge of Perdido Key “ 

Has the word Art on the front twice in big red letters .  Bathroom is directly after the entrance and to the right
comment:
Really cool shop and cool shop owners :3 bathroom is clean , has a mirror , and has AC 

 It’s a cool place to find local art too .  Owners were excited to hear about the app and welcomed the idea :3
